### User Register

POST http://localhost:4000/user-api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Shiva",
    "lastName": "Mani",
    "email": "sm@email.com",
    "password": "123456",
    "profileImageUrl": "https://example.com/avatars/user.png"
}
### User Authenticate
POST http://localhost:4000/user-api/authenticate
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email":"sm@email.com",
    "password":"123456",
    "role":"USER"
}
