### Create an Article
POST http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "author":"698973deefc92e4384013bce",
    "title":"Programming in Python",
    "category":"Data Science",
    "content":"Python is one of the primary languages to perform Data Science Applications"
}
### Read Articles by a Author
GET http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles/698973deefc92e4384013bce
### Update the Article by Author
PUT http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "author":"698973deefc92e4384013bce",
    "articleId": "69897d00a644d776839039aa",
    "title":"Programming in Python 2",
    "category":"Data Science",
    "content":"Python is one of the primary languages to perform Data Science Applications"
}
### Delete an Article
DELETE http://localhost:4000/author-api/author/698973deefc92e4384013bce/article/69897d00a644d776839039aa